{"tid":1436071,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「爬山初心」 做自己能力範圍及相信的事","createTime":"2019-08-09T08:09:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T08:40:32.000Z","uid":29823,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3dca7be9a5c24ffdbceac2be23972452335b6ba7","tid":1436071,"uid":29823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:09:56.000Z","msg":"運動行到今日，係靠每個人嘅努力，冇大台，冇人可以命令其他人行動。<br />\n<br />\n但係就機場事件，有人加劇入手搞分化，將勇武同和理非形成二元對立。<br />\n<br />\n所以專登出個post係提下大家爬山初心<br />\n<br />\n大家諗下運動至今有冇試過出現<br />\n<br />\n無差別攻擊其他人<br />\n無差別攻擊私人財產<br />\n<br />\n所以對我黎講只要唔係以上兩樣野，核彈又好，春袋又好，亦都不割蓆。<br />\n我亦都認為其他人冇資格阻止。"},{"pid":"eb9d3fc444b85d9cb25398fedc7a43b396bf42fb","tid":1436071,"uid":29823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:11:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f525588c8db0a8dc62669acc4e7ca04373135990","tid":1436071,"uid":29823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:13:33.000Z","msg":"機場事件應該交由到時現場決定"},{"pid":"52b98e1af93c49ae1ec94e2e12d40ed202731e6a","tid":1436071,"uid":29823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:13:43.000Z","msg":"機場事件應該交由到時現場決定"},{"pid":"8bed6bc37b3f356fae65044b44ffdbbe640775bf","tid":1436071,"uid":300943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:14:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d63bc115b2a519e59e5261820a2768ae48513557","tid":1436071,"uid":29823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:19:24.000Z","msg":"機場事件應該交由到時現場決定"},{"pid":"557031b6b1cfd5c94557ca0b07f2ed2dbe89a7dc","tid":1436071,"uid":29823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:31:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd192216f0f7f8f7147e6347dcfba1688801186","tid":1436071,"uid":29823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"